      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade example that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; it retains its original factory paint throughout. Inside, the cabin is an immaculate time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by double-matting since day one. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with a comprehensive binder of service receipts and original window sticker included. Recently treated with a multi-stage paint correction and ceramic coating, this car is for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
